{"tid":714211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 如果咁網上轉播世界盃拉唔拉到？","createTime":"2018-06-23T13:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T15:59:14.000Z","uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1fc784370c02ee60be01b6fd0e71ce0b7c6f94","tid":714211,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"絕大部份網上直播係用HLS (HTTP Live Streaming)技術，簡單用個node.js server就可以proxy晒全部m3u8 + ts<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Saren-Arterius/viu-proxy/blob/master/routes/stream.js\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FSaren-Arterius%2Fviu-proxy%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2Froutes%2Fstream.js&d=iGjqz4bTxluaHsUKAJ6OTsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ab9fe719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Saren-Arterius/viu-proxy/blob/master/routes/stream.js</a><br />\n<br />\nhosting方面，用bulletproof server，例如cyberbunker<br />\n條網上直播通常限香港IP，用自己部機做proxy，經ssh tunnel射d m3u8 + ts上去server<br />\n多人睇既話，就用cloudflare做cdn<br />\n<br />\n當然，domain注冊用njal.la + xmr比錢<br />\n<br />\n如果網上直播 source有watermark既話，參考<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/50735753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F50735753&d=iGjqz4bTxluaHsUKAJ6OTsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ab1adc1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/50735753</a>，用blender將成條stream拍到好似用cam影個mon咁，去del走水印<br />\n<a href=\"https://blender.stackexchange.com/questions/39508/how-to-give-an-image-or-video-a-tv-screen-effect/39509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblender.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F39508%2Fhow-to-give-an-image-or-video-a-tv-screen-effect%2F39509&d=iGjqz4bTxluaHsUKAJ6OTsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5b8bcd46\" target=\"_blank\">https://blender.stackexchange.com/questions/39508/how-to-give-an-image-or-video-a-tv-screen-effect/39509</a><br />\n<br />\n咁仲拉唔拉到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc06d738bec6cdb84825e42e575f